videos.description: Sophie Cunningham drains the 3-pointer to cut into the Mercury's deficit.

videos.headline: Mercury's arena erupts after Sophie Cunningham's 3

videos.description: Sophie Cunningham hits a nasty crossover on Diamond DeShields before knocking down the 3-pointer.

videos.headline: Cunningham puts DeShields on skates before drilling 3

videos.description: Brianna Turner loses her balance on a quick lay-in that puts the Mercury ahead.

videos.headline: Brianna Turner takes out cameramen on layup

videos.description: Courtney Vandersloot shows off her vision and finds Candace Parker for the lay-in.

videos.headline: Vandersloot drops in perfect dime to Parker for layup

videos.description: Chris Paul and Devin Booker can't contain their excitement after watching Shey Peddy score a key basket for the Mercury.

videos.headline: CP3 and Booker get hyped over Peddy's clutch lay-in

videos.description: Courtney Vandersloot goes head-to-head with Brittney Griner for the game-tying layup.

videos.headline: Vandersloot hits lay-in over Griner to send game to OT

videos.description: Skylar Diggins-Smith shows no fear and drives on Courtney Vandersloot to extend the Mercury's lead.

videos.headline: Diggins-Smith takes Vandersloot to the rack to ice the Sky

videos.description: Brittney Griner drops 29 points and Diana Taurasi adds 20 points to lift the Mercury over the Sky to tie the series.
